    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "So, I could trace this down to these lines just now:\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/1b683c5ebbcae4a77a43ff2034da406c9eb0dbc4/packages/react-instantsearch-core/src/lib/useSearchResults.ts#L26-L35\r\n\r\nIn the above case, `results` is always `null` (makes sense, I guess), but `searchIndex.getScopedResults()` is not. But because of this if-statement, it is never updated.",
